153 #define ACTION_BUTTON_ACTION(X) (uint32(X) & 0x00FFFFFF)
154 #define ACTION_BUTTON_TYPE(X) ((uint32(X) & 0xFF000000) >> 24)
155 #define MAX_ACTION_BUTTON_ACTION_VALUE (0x00FFFFFF+1)
156 
157 struct ActionButton
158 {
159  ActionButton() : packedData(0), uState(ACTIONBUTTON_NEW) {}
160 
161  uint32 packedData;
162  ActionButtonUpdateState uState;
163 
164  // helpers
165  ActionButtonType GetType() const { return ActionButtonType(ACTION_BUTTON_TYPE(packedData)); }
166  uint32 GetAction() const { return ACTION_BUTTON_ACTION(packedData); }
167  void SetActionAndType(uint32 action, ActionButtonType type)
168  {
169  uint32 newData = action | (uint32(type) << 24);
170  if (newData != packedData || uState == ACTIONBUTTON_DELETED)
171  {
172  packedData = newData;
173  if (uState != ACTIONBUTTON_NEW)
174  uState = ACTIONBUTTON_CHANGED;
175  }
176  }
177 };

307 struct LookingForGroupInfo
308 {
309  struct Slot
310  {
311  bool empty() const { return (!type || !entry); }
312  void clear() { entry = 0; }
313  bool set(uint16 _entry, uint16 _type) { entry = _entry; type = _type; return !empty(); }
314  bool is(uint16 _entry, uint16 _type) const { return entry == _entry && type == _type; }
315  bool isAuto() const { return entry && (type == LFG_TYPE_DUNGEON || type == LFG_TYPE_HEROIC_DUNGEON); }
316 
317  uint16 entry = 0;
318  uint16 type = LFG_TYPE_DUNGEON;
319  };
320 
321  inline void clear()
322  {
323  more.clear();
324  for (auto& slot : group)
325  slot.clear();
326  }
327  inline bool isAutoFill() const { return more.isAuto(); }
328  inline bool isAutoJoin() const
329  {
330  for (auto& slot : group)
331  if (slot.isAuto())
332  return true;
333  return false;
334  }
335  inline bool isEmpty() const { return (!isLFM() && !isLFG()); }
336  inline bool isLFG() const
337  {
338  for (auto& slot : group)
339  if (!slot.empty())
340  return true;
341  return false;
342  }
343  inline bool isLFG(uint32 entry, uint32 type, bool autoOnly) const
344  {
345  for (auto& slot : group)
346  if (slot.is(uint16(entry), uint16(type)) && (!autoOnly || slot.isAuto()))
347  return true;
348  return false;
349  }
350  inline bool isLFG(LookingForGroupInfo const& info, bool autoOnly) const { return isLFG(uint16(info.more.entry), uint16(info.more.type), autoOnly); }
351  inline bool isLFM() const { return !more.empty(); }
352  inline bool isLFM(uint32 entry, uint32 type) const { return more.is(uint16(entry), uint16(type)); }
353 
354  // bool queued = false;
355  Slot group[MAX_LOOKING_FOR_GROUP_SLOT];
356  Slot more;
357  std::string comment;
358 };

829  bool IsTaximaskNodeKnown(uint32 nodeidx) const
830  {
831  uint8 field = uint8((nodeidx - 1) / 32);
832  uint32 submask = 1 << ((nodeidx - 1) % 32);
833  return (m_taximask[field] & submask) == submask;
834  }
835  bool SetTaximaskNode(uint32 nodeidx)
836  {
837  uint8 field = uint8((nodeidx - 1) / 32);
838  uint32 submask = 1 << ((nodeidx - 1) % 32);
839  if ((m_taximask[field] & submask) != submask)
840  {
841  m_taximask[field] |= submask;
842  return true;
843  }
844  return false;
845  }
846  void AppendTaximaskTo(ByteBuffer& data, bool all);
847 
848  friend std::ostringstream& operator<<(std::ostringstream& ss, PlayerTaxi const& taxi);
849 
850  private:
851  TaxiMask m_taximask;
852 };

1850  template<typename T>
1851  bool CheckForGroup(T functor) const
1852  {
1853  if (Group const* group = GetGroup())
1854  {
1855  for (GroupReference const* ref = group->GetFirstMember(); ref != nullptr; ref = ref->next())
1856  {
1857  Player const* member = ref->getSource();
1858  if (member && functor(member))
1859  return true;
1860  }
1861  }
1862  else
1863  {
1864  if (functor(this))
1865  return true;
1866  }
1867  return false;
1868  }

2284  template <typename F>
2285  void RemoveSomeCooldown(F check)
2286  {
2287  auto spellCDItr = m_cooldownMap.begin();
2288  while (spellCDItr != m_cooldownMap.end())
2289  {
2290  SpellEntry const* entry = sSpellTemplate.LookupEntry<SpellEntry>(spellCDItr->first);
2291  if (entry && check(*entry))
2292  {
2293  SendClearCooldown(spellCDItr->first, this);
2294  spellCDItr = m_cooldownMap.erase(spellCDItr);
2295  }
2296  else
2297  ++spellCDItr;
2298  }
2299  }

2649 // "the bodies of template functions must be made available in a header file"
2650 template <class T> void Player::ApplySpellMod(uint32 spellId, SpellModOp op, T& basevalue, bool finalUse)
2651 {
2652  SpellEntry const* spellInfo = sSpellTemplate.LookupEntry<SpellEntry>(spellId);
2653  if (!spellInfo || spellInfo->SpellFamilyName != GetSpellClass() || spellInfo->HasAttribute(SPELL_ATTR_EX3_IGNORE_CASTER_MODIFIERS)) return; // client condition
2654  int32 totalpct = 100;
2655  int32 totalflat = 0;
2656  std::vector<SpellModifier*> consumedFiniteMods;
2657  for (SpellModifier* mod : m_spellMods[op])
2658  {
2659  if (mod->op == SPELLMOD_CASTING_TIME || mod->op == SPELLMOD_COST)
2660  if (T((basevalue + totalflat) * std::max(0, totalpct) / 100) <= 0)
2661  break;
2662 
2663  if (!IsAffectedBySpellmod(spellInfo, mod, m_consumedMods))
2664  continue;
2665  if (mod->type == SPELLMOD_FLAT)
2666  totalflat += mod->value;
2667  else if (mod->type == SPELLMOD_PCT)
2668  {
2669  // special case (skip >10sec spell casts for instant cast setting)
2670  if (mod->op == SPELLMOD_CASTING_TIME && basevalue >= T(10 * IN_MILLISECONDS) && mod->value <= -100)
2671  continue;
2672 
2673  totalpct += mod->value;
2674  }
2675 
2676  if (mod->isFinite && finalUse)
2677  {
2678  bool consume = true;
2679  if (!m_consumedMods) // If empty pointer then immediately consume
2680  {
2681  consumedFiniteMods.push_back(mod); // need to delay in order to not corrupt the list
2682  consume = false;
2683  }
2684  else if (m_consumedMods->find(SpellModifierPair(mod->spellId, mod->modId)) != m_consumedMods->end()) // if already consumed, dont consume again
2685  consume = false;
2686 
2687  if (consume)
2688  {
2689  --mod->charges;
2690  m_consumedMods->insert(SpellModifierPair(mod->spellId, mod->modId));
2691  if (!mod->charges)
2692  mod->charges = -1;
2693  }
2694  }
2695  }
2696 
2697  for (SpellModifier* mod : consumedFiniteMods)
2698  RemoveAuraCharge(mod->spellId);
2699 
2700  if (totalpct < 0)
2701  totalpct = 0;
2702 
2703  if (totalflat != 0 || totalpct != 100)
2704  basevalue = T((basevalue + totalflat) * std::max(0, totalpct) / 100);
2705 }
